PAIR_TYPE().details: Returns the pair type for volatile pairs

addLiquidity(address[],uint256[],uint256.details: Adds liquidity to a pair of tokens

params._amountDesireds: Array of desired amounts of each token
params._amountsMin: Array of minimum amounts of each token
params._deadline: Timestamp after which the transaction will revert
params._minLiquidity: Minimum amount of liquidity to mint
params._to: Address to receive the minted liquidity

returns._amounts: Amounts of tokens added to the liquidity pool

addLiquidityETH(address[],uint256[],uint.details: Adds liquidity to a pair of tokens

params._amountDesireds: Array of desired amounts of each token
params._amountsMin: Array of minimum amounts of each token
params._deadline: Timestamp after which the transaction will revert
params._minLiquidity: Minimum amount of liquidity to mint
params._to: Address to receive the minted liquidity

returns._amounts: Amounts of tokens added to the liquidity pool

params._weth: Address of the Wrapped Ether contract

factory().details: Returns the address of the factory contract

getReserves(address,address[]).details: Returns the reserves of the given pair and tokens

quoteAddLiquidity(address[],uint256[]).details: Calculates the optimal amount of token A and token B to add to a pair given desired amounts of each

params._amountDesireds: Array of desired amounts of each token

returns._amountsIn: Array of amounts of each token to add

quoteRemoveLiquidity(address[],uint256).details: Calculates the amount of tokens to receive upon removing liquidity from a pair

returns._amounts: Array of amounts of each token to receive

removeLiquidity(address[],uint256,uint25.details: Removes liquidity from a pair of tokens

params._amountsMin: Array of minimum amounts of each token to receive
params._deadline: Timestamp after which the transaction will revert

removeLiquidityETH(address[],uint256,uin.details: Removes liquidity from a pair of tokens with ETH

params._amountsMin: Array of minimum amounts of each token to receive
params._deadline: Timestamp after which the transaction will revert

removeLiquidityETHWithPermit(address[],u.details: Removes liquidity from a pair of tokens with ETH and permit functionality

params._amountsMin: Array of minimum amounts of each token to receive
params._approveMax: Whether to approve the maximum amount or not
params._deadline: Timestamp after which the transaction will revert

removeLiquidityWithPermit(address[],uint.details: Removes liquidity from a pair of tokens with permit functionality

params._amountMin: Array of minimum amounts of each token to receive
params._approveMax: Whether to approve the maximum amount or not
params._deadline: Timestamp after which the transaction will revert

swap((address,address,address),uint256,u.details: Swaps tokens according to the given route

params._amountOut: Expected amount of tokens to receive
params._deadline: Timestamp after which the transaction will revert
params._route: Route containing the pair and the token to swap from
params._to: Address to receive the swapped tokens

weth().details: Returns the address of the Wrapped Ether contract
